        public static <T extends Record> T copy(T object,
                        Geometry geometry)
        Create a copy of the data object replacing the geometry with the new geometry. If the existing geometry on the object has user data it will be cloned to the new geometry.
        Parameters:
        object - The object to copy.
        geometry - The new geometry.
        Returns:
        The copied object.
